title: Cream Corn Bisquick Casserole
directions: Spray an 8x8 baking dish with non-stick spray.
In a bowl, combine biscuit mix, egg, milk, oil, and corn.
Pour half the batter into the casserole dish.
Bake at 400 degrees 35 to 40 minutes or until the top is browned.
ingredients: 1 (4 ounce) can chopped green chiles, drained
